videos.headline: Slovis, St. Brown connect for TDs on all of USC's first-quarter possessions
videos.description: Kedon Slovis tosses a touchdown pass to Amon-Ra St. Brown on four consecutive USC possessions as the Trojans take a commanding 28-0 lead going into the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Slovis, St. Brown connect for TDs on all of USC's 1st quarter possessions) 2020/12/6 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Slovis slings 35-yard TD bomb to Vaughns
videos.description: Kedon Slovis heaves a 35-yard pass to Tyler Vaughns as he runs into the end zone to pad USC's lead.
